title: Words That Go Ping by Barbara Lasserre (.epub)
description:
Words That Go Ping: The Ridiculously Wonderful World of Onomatopoeia by Barbara Lasserre

Requirements: .ePUB reader

Overview: Barbara Lasserre takes us on a playful journey through the delightful world of words that mimic sounds. Normally relegated to children's books, cartoons and comedians, she shows how these often ancient words reveal unexpected things about the way we think, speak and act. 

A book for anyone who loves playing with words.

Genre: Non-Fiction > General
